Package: fexpr
Type: Package
Title: Tools to manipulate lazy arguments, evaluation, promises, and ... objects.
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-01-18
Author: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Description: Implements a cleaner API for manipulation of non-standard evaluation in R, covering lazy arguments, finding the calling function, and ... (varargs).
